4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals with no prior knowledge aiming to become cybersecurity specialists. The program lasts 16 weeks, featuring three live online classes each week, with a maximum class size of 16 participants. Students will gain foundational skills in Windows, Linux, networking, and server administration, alongside advanced topics such as cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence analysis. The bootcamp includes strategies for managing risks and navigating compliance standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. Upon completion, participants receive an official certificate recognized by various institutions. Course content is available in English and Spanish. 

